    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>玄幻类文字挂机冒险游戏，探索一个系统丰富且娱乐快捷的放置世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262620/extras/4347a2d66a82a50bdf0ae0596baa07d0.avif?t=1734576245\" width=400 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >少年穿越异世，一路成长，屡遭奇遇，有红颜作伴，奇宠相随，写下诸多故事……最终觉醒神器封印，迎接神魔之战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262620/extras/bf7c07a787c0e56d39b62e8e7e5e339d.avif?t=1734576245\" width=400 height=100 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提供玄幻剧情任务，探索玄幻大陆，剧情非强制体验，如果不喜欢剧情可自由游玩其他系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验丰富的游戏系统：挂机历练，副本挑战，爬塔之旅，技能养成，培养宠物，炼丹打造，钓鱼采药，打坐修仙，装备刷宝，Boss挑战、炒股刷钱、红颜好感等等</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自动化放置和手动结合，选择自己想要游玩的方式</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏机制简单易上手，前期通过轻松挂机即可快速成长，后期可通过不同装备搭配实现更深玩法</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗系统可策略可自动，击败强敌来获取极品装备</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >装备强化，装备镶嵌，装备洗练，体验从无到有的快感</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种功法，多种技能，多种丹药和宝物等你发掘</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >几十种不同的宠物供你选择，多重培养玩法，让宠物与你一起征战四方<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262620/extras/c8a413d0a90fba74e08ece1157eeb562.avif?t=1734576245\" width=400 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家们对游戏如有建议或反馈bug可加入官方群交流</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方群：812243175</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262620/extras/1fb2cfc821a70519213869a1eda8fae7.avif?t=1734576245\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262620/extras_big/1fb2cfc821a70519213869a1eda8fae7.avif?t=1734576245 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
